  "description": "Lampworking and freehand glassblowing for laboratory and technical apparatus. Torch types (Bunsen, gas-oxygen, hydrogen-oxygen). Standard products: round-bottom flasks, condensers, distillation columns, thermometers, vacuum manifolds, ampoules. Glass-to-metal seals for electrical feedthroughs. Essential for ALL chemistry lab work beyond test tubes.",
